description:
Pole dancer Exotica Jones is the smoking-hot redhead with an attitude to match who mesmerizes patrons of a local strip club with her moves and her dynamite body. It's a perfect cover for the extraordinary secret-agent/super-heroine Stripperella who is ready to spring into action fending off nasty villains and defending the defenseless faster than you can slide down a fire pole.

No obstacle is insurmountable for this hottie; even gravity seems to step aside as she leaps from the tallest of buildings and floats to the ground with a little help from her locks. She's high tech and always ready for action with devices in the most unlikely of places. Watch it buddy, don't even think about touching those puppies unless you're willing to tell the truth, the whole truth, and nothing but.

Stripperella has the flexibility of a world champion pole dancer, intelligence, superhuman stregnth, awesome jumping ability, superbly martial arts moves and an unccanny ability to use her stripper moves to incapacitate her rivials. All of this and a body that won't quit! Wow!

One never knows what Stripperella will do next, but you can bet it will be full of excitement, exposure, and extremely full of exploits!
